스터디 2번문제
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>스터디2번문제</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>라디오버튼을 클릭하면 value값을 이용해 해당 사이트로 이동해 주세요.`</h1>

    <h3>(location.href 이용)</h3>

    <label id="btn1"><input type="radio"></label>네이버</label><br>
    <label id="btn2"><input type="radio"></label>구글</label><br>
    <label id="btn3"><input type="radio"></label>w3schools</label><br>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('btn1').onclick=
        () => location.href = ('https://www.naver.com');

        document.getElementById('btn2').onclick=
        () => location.href = ('https://www.google.com');

        document.getElementById('btn3').onclick=
        () => location.href = ('https://www.w3schools.com');
    </script>
</body>
</html>
